## 🏗️ Project Components

### 1) Single-cycle CPU (`source/design/single_cycle/`)

Main top module: `cpu_top.v`

Key blocks:
- `alu.v`: arithmetic/logic operations.
- `control_unit.v`: instruction decode and control signals.
- `registers_bank.v`: register file.
- `instr_mem.v`: instruction memory.
- `data_mem.v`: data memory.

### 2) Multi-cycle CPU (`source/design/multi_cycle/`)

Alternative architecture split in control and datapath support blocks:
- `top_module.v`: integration top for multi-cycle design.
- `fsm_cu.v`: finite-state machine control unit.
- `alu.v`: ALU for multi-cycle datapath.
- `register_file.v`: register bank implementation.
- `memory.v`: memory support module.

### 3) Practice modules (`source/design/practices/`)

Collection of standalone RTL exercises and utility circuits:
- Converters (binary/gray/one-hot/one-cold)
- Counters and registers
- Adders and ALU practice
- FIFO, memory, mux, shifters, drivers and controller examples

### 4) Verification (`source/verif/`)

Unit and integration testbenches:
- `alu_test.sv`
- `control_unit_test.sv`
- `registers_bank_test.sv`
- `fifo_test.sv`
- `converter_gray_bin_test.sv`
- `cpu_top_test.sv`

Assembly programs are in `source/verif/assembly/`.

