## 📄 File Descriptions

### Single-cycle design (`source/design/single_cycle/`)

| File               | Description           |
|--------------------|-----------------------|
| `cpu_top.v`        | CPU top integration   |
| `alu.v`            | Arithmetic/logic unit |
| `control_unit.v`   | Control decode logic  |
| `registers_bank.v` | Register file         |
| `instr_mem.v`      | Instruction memory    |
| `data_mem.v`       | Data memory           |

### Multi-cycle design (`source/design/multi_cycle/`)

| File              | Description                 |
|-------------------|-----------------------------|
| `top_module.v`    | Multi-cycle top integration |
| `fsm_cu.v`        | FSM control unit            |
| `alu.v`           | ALU implementation          |
| `register_file.v` | Register file               |
| `memory.v`        | Memory block                |

### Verification (`source/verif/`)

| File                         |                     Description                                      |
|------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `cpu_top_test.sv`            | CPU integration tests (test 1-15)                                    |
| `alu_test.sv`                | ALU tests                                                            |
| `control_unit_test.sv`       | Control unit tests                                                   |
| `registers_bank_test.sv`     | Register bank tests                                                  |
| `fifo_test.sv`               | FIFO tests                                                           |
| `converter_gray_bin_test.sv` | Converter tests                                                      |
| `assembly/`                  | CPU test programs in hex format                                      |
| `assembly/*.hex`             | Test programs: regs, basic_swlw, fibonacci, fibonacci_overflow, etc. |

### Synthesis scripts (`synth/`)

| File                | Description                                      |
|---------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| `config.sh`         | Loads config from `.env` / environment variables |
| `check_env.sh`      | Environment checker                              |
| `generic_synth.sh`  | Generic synthesis flow                           |
| `specific_synth.sh` | Sky130-mapped synthesis flow                     |

